00050 
00051     unit_assert(instrument.cvParams.empty() && instrument.userParams.empty());
00052 
00053     adapter.manufacturerAndModel("dummy", "LTQ-FT");
00054     if (os_) *os_ << "manufacturer: " << adapter.manufacturer() << endl 
00055                   << "model: " << adapter.model() << endl;
00056     unit_assert(instrument.cvParams.size() == 1);
00057     unit_assert(instrument.userParams.empty());
00058     unit_assert(adapter.manufacturer() == "Thermo Scientific");
00059     unit_assert(adapter.model() == "LTQ FT");
00060 
00061     adapter.manufacturerAndModel("doobie", "420");
00062     if (os_) *os_ << "manufacturer: " << adapter.manufacturer() << endl 
00063                   << "model: " << adapter.model() << endl;
00064     unit_assert(instrument.cvParams.empty());
00065     unit_assert(instrument.userParams.size() == 2);
00066     unit_assert(adapter.manufacturer() == "doobie");
00067     unit_assert(adapter.model() == "420");
00068

00070     if (os_) *os_ << "manufacturer: " << adapter.manufacturer() << endl
